title: Darko Raca
text:
Darko Raca (born May 24, 1977) is a Bosnian-Herzegovinian <a href="Association%20football">football</a> defender who played for <a href="FK%20Sloboda%20Tuzla">Sloboda Tuzla</a> in the <a href="Bosnian%20Premier%20League">Bosnian Premier League</a>.
Beside the Bosnian clubs <a href="FK%20Kozara%20Gradi%C5%A1ka">FK Kozara Gradiška</a>, <a href="HNK%20Ora%C5%A1je">HNK Orašje</a> and <a href="FK%20Sarajevo">FK Sarajevo</a>, he had previously played with the Serbian clubs <a href="FK%20Mladost%20Apatin">FK Mladost Apatin</a> and <a href="%C4%8CSK%20Pivara">ČSK Pivara</a>, and the Swedish clubs <a href="Vasalunds%20IF">Vasalunds IF</a> and <a href="Syrianska%20FC">Syrianska FC</a>.
